    dc:description "Figures 47 - 52. Hindwing pattern and venation. 47, 48 Scantiniina subtrib. nov.: Scantinius bruchoides (Walker, 1858) (modified from Gnezdilov 2012, fig. 3) 49, 50 Vindilisina subtrib. nov.: Vindilis fornicata Stal, 1870 (modified from Gnezdilov 2018, fig. 3) 51, 52 Parahiraciina Cheng & Yang, 1991 subtrib. nov.: Tetricodes tamdaoensis Vanslembrouck & Constant, 2018 (modified from Vanslembrouck and Constant 2018, fig. 4)." ;
